## 3. SYSTEM TOKENS

### Spacing (19 tokens — Figma Variables → System → Size → Spacing — EXACT)
```
0, 2, 4, 8, 10, 12, 14, 16, 20, 24, 28, 32, 40, 48, 60, 72, 80, 100
```
Use exact values: `p-[16px]`, `gap-[24px]`, `mt-[60px]`
NOTE: 6px is NOT a spacing token. 14px and 28px ARE tokens.

### Radius (12 tokens — Figma Variables → System → Size → Radius — EXACT)
Use exact border-radius from Figma. Values:
```
0, 2, 4, 6, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 40, 48, full (9999)
```
Use: `rounded-lg` (12px), `rounded-full`, `rounded-[48px]`
NOTE: 20px is NOT a radius token. 48px IS a token.

### Stroke (4 tokens — Figma Variables → System → Size → Stroke — EXACT)
```
Stroke/100: 1px
Stroke/200: 1.2px
Stroke/300: 1.6px
Stroke/Focus ring: 2px
```
Use: `border` (1px), `border-[1.2px]`, `border-[1.6px]`, `border-2` (focus ring)

