### Hero-btn
Premium layered glow for Hero CTA button. Description: "Used for Hero, CTA"
8 layers: 1× Background blur + 5× Drop shadow + 2× Inner shadow
```
Background blur: 4px
Drop shadows (cascading soft glow):
  - X:0 Y:94 Blur:26 #C8C8C8/0%   (ambient)
  - X:0 Y:60 Blur:24 #C8C8C8/3%   (far soft)
  - X:0 Y:34 Blur:20 #C8C8C8/10%  (mid glow)
  - X:0 Y:16 Blur:16 #C8C8C8/17%  (near glow)
  - X:0 Y:4  Blur:8  #C8C8C8/19%  (tight glow)
Inner shadows (depth/bevel):
  - X:-10 Y:-10 Blur:20 #303030/10% (dark edge)
  - X:10  Y:10  Blur:16 #FFFFFF/15% (light edge)
```
Tailwind: `shadow-hero-btn backdrop-blur-[4px]` (defined in tailwind.config.ts)

