## 5. RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS (Figma Variables → Responsive)

| Breakpoint | Width  | Prefix    | H Padding | V Padding | Container | Menu Items | Menu Icon | Gesture | Phone Bar |
|------------|--------|-----------|-----------|-----------|-----------|------------|-----------|---------|-----------|
| Phone      | 412px  | default   | 16px      | 16px      | 380px     | False      | True      | True    | True      |
| Tablet     | 768px  | `md:`     | 32px      | 32px      | 704px     | False      | True      | True    | True      |
| Macbook    | 1440px | `lg:`     | 64px      | 64px      | 1312px    | True       | False     | False   | False     |
| Desktop    | 1920px | `xl:`     | 64px      | 64px      | 1792px    | True       | False     | False   | False     |

### Responsive Container Pattern:
```tsx
<div className="w-full max-w-[380px] md:max-w-[704px] lg:max-w-[1312px] xl:max-w-[1792px] mx-auto px-[16px] md:px-[32px] lg:px-[64px]">
  {children}
</div>
```

### Navbar Pattern:
- Phone & Tablet → Hamburger menu icon, no inline nav links
- Macbook & Desktop → Inline nav links, no hamburger

